4️⃣ Apply Deployment to AKS ✅

   *1 Pahle check karo ki kubectl AKS cluster se connected hai ya nahi:
   *2 Run this Command:- kubectl config current-context
   *3 Agar connected hua to yeah cluster ka name dikhega as output.
   *4 Agar connected nhi hua to yeah dikhega:- az aks get-credentials --resource-group aks20250527 --name akscluster20250527
   *5 again run this:- kubectl config current-context

   *6 Now:- Deploy App to AKS:-
      Run Command:- kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
   *7 Agar yaha tak sahi to go ahead with next step.

